00:21:09,648 --> 00:21:12,173
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>from when I was maybe two years old.</b></font>

158
00:21:44,016 --> 00:21:46,348
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Do you think it's just a dream?</b></font>

159
00:21:46,418 --> 00:21:47,685
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>No, I think it's something
that happened...</b></font>

160
00:21:47,686 --> 00:21:52,385
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>when I was living at a desert base
with my father.</b></font>

161
00:21:52,891 --> 00:21:55,951
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Anyhow, the dream goes on...</b></font>

162
00:21:56,295 --> 00:21:58,957
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>and suddenly I'm alone.</b></font>

163
00:22:34,967 --> 00:22:37,959
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>That's terrible.
You know I'd never hurt you.</b></font>

164
00:23:15,474 --> 00:23:16,805
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Hey there.</b></font>

165
00:23:18,644 --> 00:23:20,669
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>What's your name, darling?</b></font>

166
00:23:24,717 --> 00:23:27,049
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Okay. It's okay.</b></font>

167
00:25:19,164 --> 00:25:21,894
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>- I gotta talk to you, Edith.
- Bruce, stay here.</b></font>

168
00:26:43,015 --> 00:26:46,815
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>C, T, G, A...</b></font>

169
00:26:48,320 --> 00:26:49,309
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>G.</b></font>

170
00:26:51,456 --> 00:26:52,650
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Bruce.</b></font>

171
00:26:59,831 --> 00:27:01,264
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>My Bruce.</b></font>

172
00:27:11,176 --> 00:27:13,736
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Morning. Glenn dropped by.</b></font>

173
00:27:14,279 --> 00:27:17,407
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>- What's he doing here?
- You know, Dr. Krenzler...</b></font>

174
00:27:17,582 --> 00:27:20,551
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>we've never had the chance
to get to know each other properly.</b></font>

175
00:27:20,619 --> 00:27:24,851
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>It's because I don't want to get to
know you, properly or improperly.</b></font>

176
00:27:26,224 --> 00:27:27,521
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>So leave.</b></font>

177
00:27:28,360 --> 00:27:29,952
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Hey, no worries.</b></font>

178
00:27:39,004 --> 00:27:41,768
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>You know,
let me give you a little heads up.</b></font>

179
00:27:41,840 --> 00:27:46,106
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>There is a hair's breadth between
friendly offer and hostile takeover.</b></font>

180
00:27:46,812 --> 00:27:50,646
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I've done my homework. The work
you're doing here is dynamite.</b></font>

181
00:27:50,849 --> 00:27:53,545
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Gl's embedded
with technology...</b></font>

182
00:27:53,618 --> 00:27:56,587
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>that makes them instantly repairable
on the battlefield...</b></font>

183
00:27:56,655 --> 00:27:58,555
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>in our sole possession.</b></font>

184
00:27:59,091 --> 00:28:02,857
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>- That's a hell of a business.
- It's not what we're doing here.</b></font>

185
00:28:02,928 --> 00:28:05,829
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>We're doing the basic science
for everyone.</b></font>

186
00:28:08,133 --> 00:28:11,330
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>You know, someday I'm gonna
write a book and I'm gonna call it.</b></font>

187
00:28:11,403 --> 00:28:15,066
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>'When Stupid ideals Happen
to Smart Penniless Scientists.</b></font>

188
00:28:16,742 --> 00:28:20,041
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>In the meantime, Bruce,
you will be hearing from me.</b></font>

189
00:28:42,367 --> 00:28:45,461
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>- About Glenn.
- There's nothing to talk about.</b></font>

190
00:28:51,176 --> 00:28:53,736
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I just wanted to say,
don't worry about him.</b></font>

191
00:28:53,812 --> 00:28:55,336
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I'll handle it.</b></font>

192
00:28:58,183 --> 00:28:59,275
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>How?</b></font>

193
00:29:00,719 --> 00:29:02,744
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I'm gonna call my father.</b></font>

194
00:29:03,555 --> 00:29:05,819
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Ask him to exert some pressure.</b></font>

195
00:29:05,957 --> 00:29:09,222
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Last I heard, you and your father
weren't speaking.</b></font>

196
00:29:13,532 --> 00:29:15,762
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I guess now I have something
to talk with him about.</b></font>

197
00:29:16,802 --> 00:29:19,327
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I think this circuit's fried.
I don't know.</b></font>

198
00:29:19,404 --> 00:29:21,599
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Maybe you want to
come take a look at it.</b></font>

199
00:29:21,673 --> 00:29:23,698
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Okay, I'll be right there.</b></font>

200
00:29:49,701 --> 00:29:53,034
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>The gamma's too high!
Bruce, I can't stop it!</b></font>

201
00:29:56,208 --> 00:29:57,800
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Harper, get out!</b></font>

202
00:29:58,710 --> 00:29:59,938
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Get out!</b></font>

203
00:30:27,239 --> 00:30:30,140
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>- How's Harper?
- He's all right.</b></font>

204
00:30:30,575 --> 00:30:32,099
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>You saved him.</b></font>

205
00:30:32,711 --> 00:30:36,545
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I don't think he's coming back
to the lab for a while, though.</b></font>

206
00:30:41,653 --> 00:30:44,349
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I don't understand
how this is possible.</b></font>

207
00:30:45,824 --> 00:30:47,587
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>You should be dead.</b></font>

208
00:30:49,794 --> 00:30:51,227
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>They worked.</b></font>

209
00:30:51,997 --> 00:30:53,487
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>The nanomeds.</b></font>

210
00:30:54,232 --> 00:30:56,291
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I feel great. I feel like...</b></font>

211
00:30:56,368 --> 00:30:58,563
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I don't know,
they must have fixed me.</b></font>

212
00:30:58,637 --> 00:31:02,630
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>They've killed everything else
that they've come in contact with.</b></font>

213
00:31:05,210 --> 00:31:06,700
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Are you sure the doctor checked.</b></font>

214
00:31:06,778 --> 00:31:08,439
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>The doctor gave me the full workup.</b></font>

215
00:31:08,513 --> 00:31:11,539
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>He wants to know
where he can get what I'm taking.</b></font>

216
00:31:11,616 --> 00:31:13,277
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I'm 100%.</b></font>

217
00:31:14,452 --> 00:31:15,544
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>More.</b></font>

218
00:31:16,788 --> 00:31:19,689
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>- What do you mean?
- Remember my bad knee?</b></font>

219
00:31:20,792 --> 00:31:22,657
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Now it's my good knee.</b></font>

220
00:31:23,795 --> 00:31:26,127
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Bruce, this isn't funny.</b></font>

221
00:31:27,132 --> 00:31:28,861
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I was watching you.</b></font>

222
00:31:28,967 --> 00:31:32,528
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>You were gonna die and I was gonna
have to watch you die.</b></font>

223
00:31:36,408 --> 00:31:37,773
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I'm sorry.</b></font>

224
00:31:39,844 --> 00:31:41,072
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Really.</b></font>

225
00:31:42,647 --> 00:31:44,877
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I am not gonna explode, okay?</b></font>

226
00:31:45,951 --> 00:31:47,145
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Yeah.</b></font>

227
00:31:48,286 --> 00:31:50,277
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>You should get some rest.</b></font>

228
00:31:51,122 --> 00:31:52,749
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I'm fine, really.</b></font>

229
00:31:54,826 --> 00:31:56,760
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I've Never Felt Better.</b></font>

230
00:32:59,557 --> 00:33:03,015
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Your name is not Krenzler.
It's Banner.</b></font>

231
00:33:07,932 --> 00:33:10,628
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>- What?
- Your name. It's Banner.</b></font>

232
00:33:11,870 --> 00:33:13,337
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Bruce Banner.</b></font>

233
00:33:18,243 --> 00:33:21,076
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>- How did you get in here?
- L work here now.</b></font>

234
00:33:21,179 --> 00:33:23,340
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>In the labs. The late shift.</b></font>

235
00:33:24,816 --> 00:33:26,841
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>It keeps me close to you.</b></font>

236
00:33:27,686 --> 00:33:31,520
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>You always work so late yourself
with your friend, Miss Ross.</b></font>

237
00:33:32,324 --> 00:33:34,884
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>No, please. Let me.</b></font>

238
00:33:38,930 --> 00:33:40,557
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>You're not well.</b></font>

239
00:33:41,866 --> 00:33:44,164
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>You've had a terrible accident.</b></font>

240
00:33:46,271 --> 00:33:48,967
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>You're wondering why
you're still alive.</b></font>

241
00:33:51,443 --> 00:33:54,173
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>You're thinking
there's something inside.</b></font>

242
00:33:55,380 --> 00:33:57,143
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Something different.</b></font>

243
00:33:59,651 --> 00:34:01,141
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Inexplicable.</b></font>

244
00:34:03,121 --> 00:34:07,080
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I can help you understand,
if you let me.</b></font>

245
00:34:09,794 --> 00:34:11,227
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>If you'll...</b></font>

246
00:34:13,164 --> 00:34:14,563
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>forgive me.</b></font>

247
00:34:18,770 --> 00:34:20,328
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Look, mister...</b></font>

248
00:34:20,839 --> 00:34:23,774
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I'm sure I have nothing
to forgive you for...</b></font>

249
00:34:25,009 --> 00:34:28,376
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>so perhaps you should leave now.
I'll be fine.</b></font>

250
00:34:28,913 --> 00:34:30,437
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>You must know.</b></font>

251
00:34:31,516 --> 00:34:34,781
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>You may not want to believe it,
but I can see it...</b></font>

252
00:34:35,387 --> 00:34:36,854
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>in your eyes.</b></font>

253
00:34:38,223 --> 00:34:40,350
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>So much like your Mother's.</b></font>

254
00:34:41,726 --> 00:34:44,320
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Of course you're my flesh
and blood...</b></font>

255
00:34:44,796 --> 00:34:47,890
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>but then you're something else, too,
aren't you?</b></font>

256
00:34:49,367 --> 00:34:51,028
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>My physical son...</b></font>

257
00:34:52,070 --> 00:34:54,300
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>but the child of my mind, too.</b></font>

258
00:34:55,807 --> 00:34:58,173
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>No. You're lying.</b></font>

259
00:34:59,144 --> 00:35:01,135
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>My parents died
when I was a small boy.</b></font>

260
00:35:01,212 --> 00:35:03,373
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>No, that's not true.</b></font>

261
00:35:03,448 --> 00:35:05,473
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>That's what
they wanted you to believe.</b></font>

262
00:35:05,550 --> 00:35:08,713
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>The experiments, the accident,
all top-secret.</b></font>

263
00:35:08,787 --> 00:35:13,053
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>They put me away for 30 years.
30 years.</b></font>

264
00:35:15,360 --> 00:35:18,796
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Away from you. Away from our work.</b></font>

265
00:35:20,765 --> 00:35:24,826
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>But they couldn't keep me forever.
I'm sane. They had to admit it.</b></font>

266
00:35:27,272 --> 00:35:28,637
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>You see...</b></font>

267
00:35:29,641 --> 00:35:33,509
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>everything your
extraordinary mind...</b></font>

268
00:35:34,212 --> 00:35:36,737
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>has been seeking all these years...</b></font>

269
00:35:37,816 --> 00:35:39,647
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>it's been inside you.</b></font>

270
00:35:40,518 --> 00:35:44,614
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Now we will understand it.
We will harness it.</b></font>

271
00:35:47,425 --> 00:35:49,791
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Don't answer. It's Miss Ross again.</b></font>

272
00:35:49,861 --> 00:35:52,557
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>There's something
you need to know about her, Bruce...</b></font>

273
00:35:52,630 --> 00:35:54,461
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>something troublesome.</b></font>

274
00:35:54,532 --> 00:35:56,693
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Let me protect you from her.</b></font>

275
00:35:57,402 --> 00:35:59,393
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>No. Get out.</b></font>

276
00:36:00,939 --> 00:36:02,201
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Get out!</b></font>

277
00:36:02,674 --> 00:36:03,732
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Sit!</b></font>

278
00:36:21,526 --> 00:36:24,620
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>We're gonna have to watch
that temper of yours.</b></font>

279
00:37:04,736 --> 00:37:08,103
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>- Sure you're okay?
- Yeah, just glad to be out of bed.</b></font>

280
00:37:09,407 --> 00:37:13,673
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I got a message from my father.
He's coming to see me.</b></font>

281
00:37:14,913 --> 00:37:16,608
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Your father? When?</b></font>

282
00:37:17,949 --> 00:37:19,974
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>He lands in about an hour.</b></font>

283
00:37:20,752 --> 00:37:23,152
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>The funny thing is, he called me.</b></font>

284
00:37:34,732 --> 00:37:36,962
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>- Hi, Dad.
- Hello, Betty.</b></font>

285
00:37:47,512 --> 00:37:49,036
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>- Here, ma'am.
- Thanks.</b></font>

286
00:37:49,113 --> 00:37:50,444
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>You're welcome. Sir.</b></font>

287
00:37:50,515 --> 00:37:52,642
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>- Thank you.
- You're welcome.</b></font>

288
00:38:01,693 --> 00:38:06,357
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>- Look, I'm gonna get right to it.
- It's about Glenn, isn't it?</b></font>

289
00:38:08,166 --> 00:38:10,532
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>He's been snooping around my lab.</b></font>

290
00:38:10,602 --> 00:38:14,868
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Glenn noticed some things.
He asked me to make some inquiries.</b></font>

291
00:38:18,376 --> 00:38:21,777
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>- Are you here to question me?
- No.</b></font>

292
00:38:23,448 --> 00:38:26,076
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>We've turned up
some surprising things.</b></font>

293
00:38:28,720 --> 00:38:30,950
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>This Krenzler you work with...</b></font>

294
00:38:31,789 --> 00:38:33,984
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>do you know who he really is?</b></font>

295
00:38:34,826 --> 00:38:37,522
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>How much do you actually know
about him?</b></font>

296
00:38:38,262 --> 00:38:40,287
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I think the question is...</b></font>

297
00:38:40,765 --> 00:38:43,256
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>what is it that you know about him?</b></font>

298
00:38:45,737 --> 00:38:47,102
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I'm not at Liberty to.</b></font>

299
00:38:47,171 --> 00:38:50,368
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Not at Liberty
to disclose it to me. Right.</b></font>

300
00:38:52,510 --> 00:38:55,345
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>You know, I think I was hoping...</b></font>

301
00:38:55,346 --> 00:39:01,808
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>that maybe this time you just
honestly wanted to see me again.</b></font>

302
00:39:03,121 --> 00:39:04,952
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>You've got this all wrong, Betty.</b></font>

303
00:39:05,023 --> 00:39:06,718
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>- Do I?
- Yes.</b></font>

304
00:39:08,126 --> 00:39:09,957
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I do want to see you.</b></font>

305
00:39:12,330 --> 00:39:14,958
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I really wish
that I could believe you.</b></font>

306
00:40:03,581 --> 00:40:07,108
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Everything your extraordinary mind...</b></font>

307
00:40:07,185 --> 00:40:10,211
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>has been seeking all these years...</b></font>

308
00:40:10,755 --> 00:40:12,552
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>it's been inside you.</b></font>

309
00:40:32,510 --> 00:40:34,307
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>This is Dr. Krenzler.</b></font>

310
00:40:34,378 --> 00:40:37,472
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Please leave a message
and I'll call you right back.</b></font>

311
00:40:38,950 --> 00:40:41,384
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Bruce, hey. Are you there?</b></font>

312
00:40:43,121 --> 00:40:45,555
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Look, I think I screwed up.</b></font>

313
00:40:45,623 --> 00:40:49,252
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>My father, it's like
he suspects you of something.</b></font>

314
00:40:50,795 --> 00:40:52,990
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I was so impatient, like always...</b></font>

315
00:40:53,064 --> 00:40:55,555
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I didn't hear him out. I don't know.</b></font>

316
00:40:55,967 --> 00:40:59,130
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I just think they're planning
something with the lab.</b></font>

317
00:41:01,706 --> 00:41:03,765
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>So call me, okay? Bye.</b></font>

318
00:41:06,878 --> 00:41:07,867
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Betty!</b></font>

319
00:42:45,443 --> 00:42:48,207
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Dispatch! We have a 4-15 at the lab!</b></font>

320
00:42:48,279 --> 00:42:50,577
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Send the Berkeley P.D. now!</b></font>

321
00:44:26,777 --> 00:44:28,404
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>What's going on?</b></font>

322
00:44:29,513 --> 00:44:32,209
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>- L gotta talk to you.
- Bruce, stay here.</b></font>

323
00:45:04,815 --> 00:45:06,305
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>My Bruce.</b></font>

324
00:45:21,165 --> 00:45:22,154
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Bruce?</b></font>

325
00:45:59,570 --> 00:46:01,902
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>There was some sort of explosion.</b></font>

326
00:46:01,972 --> 00:46:04,497
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>They wouldn't let us
into the building.</b></font>

327
00:46:05,843 --> 00:46:07,811
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I was worried about you.</b></font>

328
00:46:09,647 --> 00:46:10,909
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I'm okay.</b></font>

329
00:46:12,850 --> 00:46:15,182
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>What happened to you last night?</b></font>

330
00:46:16,454 --> 00:46:18,547
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I had the most vivid dream.</b></font>

331
00:46:21,025 --> 00:46:22,925
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>It was like being born.</b></font>

332
00:46:23,060 --> 00:46:27,224
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Coming up for air.
Light hitting my face. Screaming.</b></font>

333
00:46:28,999 --> 00:46:32,127
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>My heartbeat was like...</b></font>

334
00:46:32,236 --> 00:46:33,225
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>boom...</b></font>

335
00:46:35,139 --> 00:46:36,231
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>boom...</b></font>

336
00:46:38,843 --> 00:46:40,037
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>boom.</b></font>

337
00:46:46,317 --> 00:46:48,080
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Were you at the lab?</b></font>

338
00:46:48,953 --> 00:46:49,942
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>No.</b></font>

339
00:46:51,388 --> 00:46:53,049
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>But something...</b></font>

340
00:46:55,993 --> 00:46:59,451
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>And there was that man.
The one with the dogs.</b></font>

341
00:47:00,297 --> 00:47:01,457
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Who?</b></font>

342
00:47:03,134 --> 00:47:04,795
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>That new janitor.</b></font>

343
00:47:06,036 --> 00:47:08,027
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>He said he was my father.</b></font>

344
00:47:14,011 --> 00:47:15,410
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I'll get it.</b></font>

345
00:47:25,823 --> 00:47:27,154
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>My father.</b></font>

346
00:47:36,667 --> 00:47:37,861
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>My, my.</b></font>

347
00:47:39,737 --> 00:47:41,967
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>So this is the young Bruce Banner.</b></font>

348
00:47:44,308 --> 00:47:45,570
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Krenzler.</b></font>

349
00:47:47,912 --> 00:47:51,109
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I think you left something
in your lab last night.</b></font>

350
00:47:54,919 --> 00:47:55,908
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Mitchell.</b></font>

351
00:47:56,053 --> 00:47:59,250
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Escort my daughter outside.
I'll join her shortly.</b></font>

352
00:48:00,591 --> 00:48:03,116
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>- I'd rather stay here.
- Now, Betty.</b></font>

353
00:48:06,530 --> 00:48:09,590
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>It's okay. I'll be fine.</b></font>

354
00:48:20,878 --> 00:48:23,608
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Keep him under observation.
I'll be back.</b></font>

355
00:48:31,288 --> 00:48:33,518
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>- What?
- Your friend in there...</b></font>

356
00:48:34,258 --> 00:48:37,716
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>there's a good chance
he's caught up in some bad business.</b></font>

357
00:48:37,895 --> 00:48:39,658
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Unfinished business.</b></font>

358
00:48:40,497 --> 00:48:43,489
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I promise you, I'm going to
get to the bottom of it.</b></font>

359
00:48:43,567 --> 00:48:46,092
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>You have my word
I'll make sure he's cared for.</b></font>

360
00:48:46,170 --> 00:48:48,866
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>But as of right now,
he's incommunicado.</b></font>

361
00:48:49,206 --> 00:48:51,572
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>For the next few days at least...</b></font>

362
00:48:51,642 --> 00:48:55,100
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>you're going to stay away from here,
for your own good.</b></font>

363
00:49:04,054 --> 00:49:07,046
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>And that's for the new guy
on the night shift?</b></font>

364
00:49:07,491 --> 00:49:10,016
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Great. Thank you. I appreciate it.</b></font>

365
00:49:31,382 --> 00:49:34,977
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>How unexpected. Please, come in.</b></font>

366
00:49:40,391 --> 00:49:44,088
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I'm sorry to show up
at your house like this.</b></font>

367
00:49:49,199 --> 00:49:51,531
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I came to ask you something...</b></font>

368
00:49:52,236 --> 00:49:54,830
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>that I really have
no business asking.</b></font>

369
00:49:57,174 --> 00:49:58,573
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>He told you?</b></font>

370
00:49:59,576 --> 00:50:01,601
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>He said you talked to him.</b></font>

371
00:50:03,314 --> 00:50:04,941
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Please, sit down.</b></font>

372
00:50:13,924 --> 00:50:16,119
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Bruce was at the lab last night.</b></font>

373
00:50:16,193 --> 00:50:19,594
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>He said that you were there, too,
but he can't remember much about it.</b></font>

374
00:50:20,798 --> 00:50:23,198
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I need to find out what happened.</b></font>

375
00:50:23,400 --> 00:50:26,563
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>So you want to know
what's wrong with him.</b></font>

376
00:50:27,905 --> 00:50:32,205
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>So you can fix him.
Cure him. Change him.</b></font>

377
00:50:34,478 --> 00:50:36,708
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>My father's with the military.</b></font>

378
00:50:37,114 --> 00:50:41,278
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>He thinks he's involved in some
kind of threat to national security.</b></font>

379
00:50:42,453 --> 00:50:44,751
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Your father, Ross.</b></font>

380
00:50:46,724 --> 00:50:50,285
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>You brought your father
down upon his head.</b></font>

381
00:50:50,961 --> 00:50:53,452
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>How little you understand,
Miss Ross.</b></font>

382
00:50:53,530 --> 00:50:56,522
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>And how dangerous
your ignorance has become.</b></font>

383
00:50:59,069 --> 00:51:01,401
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>- I'm sorry?
- Don't be sorry.</b></font>

384
00:51:02,139 --> 00:51:05,700
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>My son is... unique.</b></font>

385
00:51:06,777 --> 00:51:09,268
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>That's why you can't relate to him.</b></font>

386
00:51:09,546 --> 00:51:11,275
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>And because he is unique...</b></font>

387
00:51:11,348 --> 00:51:14,909
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>the world will not tolerate
his existence, will they?</b></font>

388
00:51:16,620 --> 00:51:18,178
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>But you...</b></font>

389
00:51:20,491 --> 00:51:23,324
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>you try, don't you?</b></font>

390
00:51:31,468 --> 00:51:34,437
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>And a very beautiful woman
like you...</b></font>

391
00:51:35,472 --> 00:51:37,133
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>your attentions...</b></font>

392
00:51:37,875 --> 00:51:41,038
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>can't be completely unwanted...</b></font>

393
00:51:42,379 --> 00:51:43,641
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>can they?</b></font>

394
00:51:45,249 --> 00:51:46,273
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>No.</b></font>

395
00:51:47,584 --> 00:51:50,212
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Not with eyes like yours...</b></font>

396
00:51:51,655 --> 00:51:55,921
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>watching expectantly, lovingly.</b></font>

397
00:51:59,630 --> 00:52:02,690
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>But I'm afraid
we're both too late to help him.</b></font>

398
00:52:02,833 --> 00:52:06,769
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>There's nothing I can do for him,
or for you.</b></font>

399
00:52:08,071 --> 00:52:09,402
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Besides...</b></font>

400
00:52:10,407 --> 00:52:13,240
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>he's made it clear
he wants nothing to do with me.</b></font>

401
00:52:13,310 --> 00:52:14,675
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>His choice.</b></font>

402
00:52:15,045 --> 00:52:18,742
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Now if you'll excuse me, Miss Ross,
I have some work to do.</b></font>

403
00:52:19,716 --> 00:52:22,116
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>And don't worry about the dogs.</b></font>

404
00:52:22,553 --> 00:52:26,182
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>You'll be fine.
Just don't look them in the eyes.</b></font>

405
00:52:29,860 --> 00:52:31,088
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Goodbye.</b></font>

406
00:52:33,564 --> 00:52:36,658
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>He gets released, and a month later
your lab is destroyed.</b></font>

407
00:52:36,733 --> 00:52:38,257
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>What a coincidence.</b></font>

408
00:52:38,335 --> 00:52:41,065
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>So, you're just not gonna tell me
where he is, are you?</b></font>

409
00:52:41,138 --> 00:52:42,799
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>How many times must I tell you...</b></font>

410
00:52:42,873 --> 00:52:44,966
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I want to help you,
but I don't know.</b></font>

411
00:52:45,042 --> 00:52:47,067
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>You know who I am, right, Banner?</b></font>

412
00:52:47,144 --> 00:52:49,339
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>You're Betty's father,
a high-ranking general.</b></font>

413
00:52:49,413 --> 00:52:50,710
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Let's cut the crap.</b></font>

414
00:52:50,781 --> 00:52:54,148
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I'm the guy
who had your father tossed away.</b></font>

415
00:52:54,218 --> 00:52:57,847
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I'll do the same with you if I feel
so disposed, you understand?</b></font>

416
00:52:57,921 --> 00:53:02,255
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>If you had him tossed away,
why ask me? I don't remember.</b></font>

417
00:53:02,392 --> 00:53:04,292
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I was always told
my father was dead.</b></font>

418
00:53:04,361 --> 00:53:06,090
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Don't play with me!</b></font>

419
00:53:06,263 --> 00:53:08,823
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>You were four years old
when you saw it!</b></font>

420
00:53:10,133 --> 00:53:11,498
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>When I saw what?</b></font>

421
00:53:11,568 --> 00:53:15,129
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>You were right there!
Who could forget a thing like that?</b></font>

422
00:53:17,441 --> 00:53:18,533
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>What?</b></font>

423
00:53:19,643 --> 00:53:21,838
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Some more repressed memories.</b></font>

424
00:53:25,349 --> 00:53:26,816
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Just tell me.</b></font>

425
00:53:29,920 --> 00:53:31,444
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I'm sorry, son.</b></font>

426
00:53:33,123 --> 00:53:36,854
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>You're an even more screwed-up mess
than I thought you'd be.</b></font>

427
00:53:37,828 --> 00:53:40,023
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Till we get to the bottom of this...</b></font>

428
00:53:40,097 --> 00:53:43,089
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>your lab has been declared
a top-secret military site...</b></font>

429
00:53:43,166 --> 00:53:46,260
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>and you won't get security clearance
to get back into it...</b></font>

430
00:53:46,336 --> 00:53:49,601
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>or any other lab that's doing
anything more interesting than...</b></font>

431
00:53:49,840 --> 00:53:53,571
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>trying to figure out the next
generation of herbal hair gel.</b></font>

432
00:53:56,680 --> 00:53:58,409
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>And one more thing</b></font>

433
00:53:59,216 --> 00:54:03,152
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>if you ever come
within a thousand yards...</b></font>

434
00:54:03,220 --> 00:54:05,085
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>of my daughter again...</b></font>

435
00:54:05,522 --> 00:54:08,821
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I'll put you away
for the rest of your natural life.</b></font>

436
00:54:23,307 --> 00:54:24,433
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Dogs?</b></font>

437
00:54:27,311 --> 00:54:28,335
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Go!</b></font>

438
00:54:29,279 --> 00:54:32,976
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Go get her!
And let nothing stand in your way!</b></font>

439
00:55:40,283 --> 00:55:42,217
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>- Hello?
- Bruce?</b></font>

440
00:55:43,520 --> 00:55:47,251
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>So, they think they can just
throw you away, as they did me.</b></font>

441
00:55:56,166 --> 00:55:58,964
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>What's wrong with me?
What did you do to me?</b></font>

442
00:55:59,036 --> 00:56:00,503
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I had a visit today.</b></font>

443
00:56:00,570 --> 00:56:02,765
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>A very unwelcome visit.</b></font>

444
00:56:03,440 --> 00:56:05,965
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I'm afraid my hand is being forced.</b></font>

445
00:56:06,643 --> 00:56:08,736
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>What did you do to me?</b></font>

446
00:56:09,746 --> 00:56:12,271
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>You so much want to know,
don't you?</b></font>

447
00:56:12,816 --> 00:56:17,719
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>But no explanation will serve you
half as well as experience.</b></font>

448
00:56:19,756 --> 00:56:23,192
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>In any case, I still don't
quite understand it myself.</b></font>

449
00:56:23,960 --> 00:56:26,394
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>If they'd only let me work in peace.</b></font>

450
00:56:26,630 --> 00:56:29,895
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>But, of course, my betters
would have none of that.</b></font>

451
00:56:30,267 --> 00:56:33,168
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>So you experimented on yourself,
didn't you?</b></font>

452
00:56:33,236 --> 00:56:35,704
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>And passed on to me, what?</b></font>

453
00:56:36,907 --> 00:56:38,932
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>An alteration. Genetic.</b></font>

454
00:56:39,776 --> 00:56:42,643
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>A deformity,
I guess you could call it that.</b></font>

455
00:56:43,647 --> 00:56:45,945
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>But an amazing strength, too.</b></font>

456
00:56:46,750 --> 00:56:50,049
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>And now, finally unleashed,
I can harvest it.</b></font>

457
00:56:50,787 --> 00:56:51,776
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>No.</b></font>

458
00:56:51,855 --> 00:56:55,621
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>You'll do no such thing.
I'll isolate it and treat myself.</b></font>

459
00:56:55,859 --> 00:56:59,192
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I'll remove it and kill it
before it does any real harm.</b></font>

460
00:56:59,262 --> 00:57:02,459
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I bet you and your Betty
would love to destroy it.</b></font>

461
00:57:02,599 --> 00:57:05,591
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>But would you really destroy
part of yourself?</b></font>

462
00:57:06,770 --> 00:57:08,362
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I don't think so.</b></font>

463
00:57:09,372 --> 00:57:10,930
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>And as for Betty...</b></font>

464
00:57:11,374 --> 00:57:15,708
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I'm sending her a surprise visit
from my four-legged friends.</b></font>

465
00:57:16,079 --> 00:57:20,209
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>You see, I've managed to culture
some of your very own DNA, Bruce...</b></font>

466
00:57:20,717 --> 00:57:23,015
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>and the results are tremendous.</b></font>

467
00:57:23,320 --> 00:57:26,312
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>They're unstable, but very powerful.</b></font>

468
00:57:28,525 --> 00:57:30,186
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>What about my DNA?</b></font>

469
00:57:31,428 --> 00:57:34,886
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Let's just wait and see
what Betty makes of the result.</b></font>

470
00:57:35,065 --> 00:57:38,501
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>No. You're crazy. I won't let you.</b></font>

471
00:57:42,305 --> 00:57:44,170
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Get your hands off me!</b></font>

472
00:57:44,508 --> 00:57:47,136
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Inside, asshole!
I want to talk to you.</b></font>

473
00:57:47,244 --> 00:57:49,303
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>My father's going after Betty.</b></font>

474
00:57:49,379 --> 00:57:51,472
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Do you think you can go
behind my back...</b></font>

475
00:57:51,548 --> 00:57:53,641
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>and get Ross to cut me out?</b></font>

476
00:57:54,184 --> 00:57:56,550
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Listen to me! Betty's in trouble!</b></font>

477
00:57:59,222 --> 00:58:00,655
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>You pathetic freak.</b></font>

478
00:58:00,724 --> 00:58:02,817
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Betty's in danger, I swear to you.</b></font>

479
00:58:02,893 --> 00:58:06,090
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>If I can state the obvious,
something tells me...</b></font>

480
00:58:06,163 --> 00:58:10,122
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>you aren't in much of a position to
be making stupid threats to anyone.</b></font>

481
00:58:13,937 --> 00:58:15,632
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>- Talbot.
- Yeah?</b></font>

482
00:58:16,106 --> 00:58:19,507
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>- You're making me angry.
- Am I?</b></font>

483
00:59:16,166 --> 00:59:18,361
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Open fire!</b></font>

484
01:01:09,612 --> 01:01:10,874
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>BRUCE?</b></font>

485
01:06:37,840 --> 01:06:39,967
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>He sent his dogs, didn't he?</b></font>

486
01:06:41,444 --> 01:06:43,105
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>But I killed them.</b></font>

487
01:07:08,571 --> 01:07:09,936
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Oh, my God.</b></font>

488
01:07:10,406 --> 01:07:13,102
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>It must be the nanomeds.
It must be the gamma exposure.</b></font>

489
01:07:13,176 --> 01:07:16,270
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>But we've never seen any effect
like this before.</b></font>

490
01:07:16,346 --> 01:07:18,041
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>No. Deeper.</b></font>

491
01:07:19,182 --> 01:07:21,742
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>The gamma just unleashed
what was already there.</b></font>

492
01:07:21,818 --> 01:07:23,342
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Unleashed what?</b></font>

493
01:07:25,388 --> 01:07:26,412
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Me.</b></font>

494
01:07:27,790 --> 01:07:28,814
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Lt.</b></font>

495
01:07:31,861 --> 01:07:33,192
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>it's okay.</b></font>

496
01:07:36,966 --> 01:07:38,934
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>What were those animals?</b></font>

497
01:07:39,769 --> 01:07:41,532
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>My father sent them.</b></font>

498
01:07:42,505 --> 01:07:44,097
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>He is my father.</b></font>

499
01:07:45,408 --> 01:07:47,308
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>He wanted me to change.</b></font>

500
01:07:47,377 --> 01:07:50,437
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>He wanted me to change
into that mindless hulk.</b></font>

501
01:07:50,780 --> 01:07:52,839
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>And why would he want that?</b></font>

502
01:07:54,417 --> 01:07:56,442
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Can you remember anything?</b></font>

503
01:07:56,519 --> 01:07:59,454
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Is there anything
from when you were changed?</b></font>

504
01:08:02,792 --> 01:08:04,555
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>It was like a dream.</b></font>

505
01:08:06,295 --> 01:08:07,660
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>About what?</b></font>

506
01:08:10,032 --> 01:08:11,124
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Rage.</b></font>

507
01:08:13,603 --> 01:08:14,763
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Power.</b></font>

508
01:08:16,906 --> 01:08:18,305
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>And freedom.</b></font>

509
01:08:38,361 --> 01:08:39,419
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Hello.</b></font>

510
01:08:39,996 --> 01:08:41,054
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Sir.</b></font>

511
01:08:42,098 --> 01:08:43,190
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Hello.</b></font>

512
01:08:43,266 --> 01:08:45,826
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>- Dad?
- Betty, are you all right?</b></font>

513
01:08:48,771 --> 01:08:50,136
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I'm scared.</b></font>

514
01:08:51,140 --> 01:08:53,540
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>- I need your help.
- Where are you?</b></font>

515
01:09:04,921 --> 01:09:06,320
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>How are you?</b></font>

516
01:09:07,356 --> 01:09:09,347
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Okay, I guess.</b></font>

517
01:09:13,729 --> 01:09:18,223
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I think that somehow your anger
is triggering the nanomeds.</b></font>

518
01:09:20,269 --> 01:09:23,796
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>How could it? We designed them
to respond to physical damage.</b></font>

519
01:09:23,873 --> 01:09:26,603
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Emotional damage
can manifest physically.</b></font>

520
01:09:28,444 --> 01:09:29,775
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Like what?</b></font>

521
01:09:33,850 --> 01:09:35,374
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Serious trauma.</b></font>

522
01:09:37,987 --> 01:09:39,716
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Repressed memories.</b></font>

523
01:09:45,094 --> 01:09:47,824
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Your father grilled me
about something...</b></font>

524
01:09:47,897 --> 01:09:50,331
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>that happened to me
from early childhood...</b></font>

525
01:09:50,399 --> 01:09:52,629
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>that I'm supposed to remember.</b></font>

526
01:09:53,002 --> 01:09:55,061
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>- He did?
- Lt sounded bad...</b></font>

527
01:09:56,906 --> 01:09:59,136
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>but I honestly don't remember.</b></font>

528
01:10:02,411 --> 01:10:04,846
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>The thing that worries me...</b></font>

529
01:10:04,847 --> 01:10:09,250
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>is a physical wound is finite.</b></font>

530
01:10:09,852 --> 01:10:13,982
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>But with emotions, what's to say
that it won't just go on and on...</b></font>

531
01:10:15,057 --> 01:10:17,150
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>and start a chain reaction?</b></font>

532
01:10:20,863 --> 01:10:23,263
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>You know what scares me the most?</b></font>

533
01:10:25,368 --> 01:10:27,393
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Ls that when it happens...</b></font>

534
01:10:28,538 --> 01:10:32,201
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>when it comes over me
and I totally lose control...</b></font>

535
01:10:35,545 --> 01:10:36,876
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I like it.</b></font>

536
01:10:54,397 --> 01:10:57,127
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>it's okay, I've got you. I'm sorry.</b></font>

537
01:10:58,734 --> 01:11:01,396
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>You'll be okay.
It's just to make you sleep.</b></font>

538
01:11:01,470 --> 01:11:03,597
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>- Target down.
- Target secure.</b></font>

539
01:11:04,073 --> 01:11:06,803
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I'm gonna take you
someplace safe, okay?</b></font>

540
01:11:07,209 --> 01:11:09,973
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Bruce. Bruce.</b></font>

541
01:13:59,815 --> 01:14:02,010
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>- Attention on deck.
- Carry on.</b></font>

542
01:14:10,926 --> 01:14:13,417
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>We're buried out here
in the middle of nowhere.</b></font>

543
01:14:13,496 --> 01:14:15,555
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>How long are you gonna
keep him sedated?</b></font>

544
01:14:15,631 --> 01:14:17,963
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>For the rest of his natural life,
if I have to.</b></font>

545
01:14:18,033 --> 01:14:21,025
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>- You said I could trust you.
- I'm your father.</b></font>

546
01:14:21,504 --> 01:14:24,132
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Trust me to do
what I think is right...</b></font>

547
01:14:24,206 --> 01:14:25,764
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>not what you think you want.</b></font>

548
01:14:25,841 --> 01:14:29,299
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>- He is a human being.
- He is also something else.</b></font>

549
01:14:29,712 --> 01:14:31,475
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Suppose he gets out...</b></font>

550
01:14:31,547 --> 01:14:34,675
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>and has one of his little
mood swings in a populated area?</b></font>

551
01:14:34,750 --> 01:14:37,014
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Yes, I'm aware
of the potential danger.</b></font>

552
01:14:37,086 --> 01:14:39,281
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I'm also aware
that he saved my life.</b></font>

553
01:14:39,355 --> 01:14:41,789
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Yeah, from a mutant French poodle.</b></font>

554
01:14:42,491 --> 01:14:44,686
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I'm indebted to him for that.</b></font>

555
01:14:44,860 --> 01:14:48,455
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>He also put three men in a hospital,
and Talbot's barely walking.</b></font>

556
01:14:48,531 --> 01:14:52,262
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>- I mean, what do you want me to do?
- I want you to help him!</b></font>

557
01:14:52,635 --> 01:14:54,466
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Why is he such a threat to you?</b></font>

558
01:14:54,537 --> 01:14:56,630
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Because I know what he comes from.</b></font>

559
01:14:56,705 --> 01:15:00,937
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>He is his father's son,
every last molecule of him.</b></font>

560
01:15:01,477 --> 01:15:03,502
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>He says he doesn't know his father.</b></font>

561
01:15:03,579 --> 01:15:07,879
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>But he's working in the same,
exact goddamn field his father did.</b></font>

562
01:15:09,185 --> 01:15:12,586
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>So either he's lying,
or it's something worse...</b></font>

563
01:15:12,855 --> 01:15:14,584
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>- And he's...
- What?</b></font>

564
01:15:15,491 --> 01:15:18,585
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Predestined to follow
in his father's footsteps?</b></font>

565
01:15:20,863 --> 01:15:22,990
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I was going to say 'damned.</b></font>

566
01:15:24,433 --> 01:15:26,162
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Of course you were.</b></font>

567
01:15:26,502 --> 01:15:29,232
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>But I'm a scientist,
and as a scientist...</b></font>

568
01:15:29,305 --> 01:15:32,741
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I believe we can figure this out
and he can be helped.</b></font>

569
01:15:32,908 --> 01:15:34,398
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I know you do.</b></font>

570
01:15:36,178 --> 01:15:38,578
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Look, whether you know or care...</b></font>

571
01:15:40,449 --> 01:15:43,350
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I've got a lot of pride
in what you've done.</b></font>

572
01:15:43,853 --> 01:15:45,980
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>But this is too big for you.</b></font>

573
01:15:46,322 --> 01:15:50,554
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Look, I know the government thinks
they have a weapon on their hands...</b></font>

574
01:15:50,626 --> 01:15:52,821
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>otherwise, he'd be dead by now.</b></font>

575
01:15:52,895 --> 01:15:55,056
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>They can probe and prod
all they want.</b></font>

576
01:15:55,130 --> 01:15:59,362
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Meanwhile, let me try to help him.
Nobody knows him better than I do.</b></font>

577
01:16:03,839 --> 01:16:06,171
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>What did David Banner do to him?</b></font>

578
01:16:10,813 --> 01:16:13,373
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Cover left! Cover right!</b></font>

579
01:18:25,180 --> 01:18:27,045
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>What's happening here?</b></font>

580
01:18:28,150 --> 01:18:29,378
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>My hand.</b></font>

581
01:18:31,920 --> 01:18:35,151
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>You see,
the strength of my son's DNA...</b></font>

582
01:18:36,959 --> 01:18:40,725
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>combined with
nanomed reconstruction...</b></font>

583
01:18:43,165 --> 01:18:46,657
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>You see, I can partake
with the essences of all things.</b></font>

584
01:18:49,004 --> 01:18:53,168
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I'm gonna have to ask you
to put your hands up, pal, okay?</b></font>

585
01:18:54,743 --> 01:18:56,233
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Nice and easy.</b></font>

586
01:19:02,951 --> 01:19:07,684
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Do you really believe
that I am separate from you?</b></font>

587
01:19:26,909 --> 01:19:28,274
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Where am I?</b></font>

588
01:19:33,015 --> 01:19:34,414
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>You're home.</b></font>

589
01:19:47,296 --> 01:19:50,094
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>It's hard to believe
we used to live here.</b></font>

590
01:19:52,568 --> 01:19:55,002
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I must have seen you or known you.</b></font>

591
01:19:56,038 --> 01:19:58,029
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>If only I could remember.</b></font>

592
01:20:32,541 --> 01:20:34,839
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>This is my old house, isn't it?</b></font>

593
01:21:14,850 --> 01:21:16,112
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Let's go.</b></font>

594
01:21:17,819 --> 01:21:19,184
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Please try.</b></font>

595
01:22:13,809 --> 01:22:16,835
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>- What is it?
- Nothing.</b></font>

596
01:22:18,614 --> 01:22:19,808
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Really?</b></font>

597
01:22:23,185 --> 01:22:24,413
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Damn it.</b></font>

598
01:22:29,825 --> 01:22:33,386
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Okay, Betty.
What do you want to know?</b></font>

599
01:22:37,165 --> 01:22:39,030
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>What was in that room?</b></font>

600
01:22:50,145 --> 01:22:52,579
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>What are you afraid that I'll see?</b></font>

601
01:22:58,654 --> 01:23:01,521
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>See? There's nothing.</b></font>

602
01:23:03,525 --> 01:23:04,890
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>It's empty.</b></font>

603
01:23:17,739 --> 01:23:19,866
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>What do you mean
I don't have access to him?</b></font>

604
01:23:19,941 --> 01:23:24,207
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>NSA has decided to turn over
study of the threat...</b></font>

605
01:23:24,946 --> 01:23:26,277
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>to Atheon.</b></font>

606
01:23:27,115 --> 01:23:30,744
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>But you're head of the base.
I thought you were in charge.</b></font>

607
01:23:30,919 --> 01:23:32,386
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I don't set policy.</b></font>

608
01:23:32,688 --> 01:23:34,656
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>And I still take orders.</b></font>

609
01:23:37,726 --> 01:23:40,627
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I can't believe
Talbot would go around me like this!</b></font>

610
01:23:43,732 --> 01:23:47,133
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>There's a lot of powerful people
who want in on this...</b></font>

611
01:23:47,202 --> 01:23:49,397
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>and money to be made, lots of it.</b></font>

612
01:23:55,644 --> 01:23:57,805
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Know the worst part about all this?</b></font>

613
01:23:58,914 --> 01:24:01,644
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>When I had David Banner locked up
and sent that kid away...</b></font>

614
01:24:01,717 --> 01:24:03,412
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I didn't give the boy
a second thought.</b></font>

615
01:24:03,485 --> 01:24:05,248
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>He was just collateral damage.</b></font>

616
01:24:06,154 --> 01:24:08,122
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>He isn't anymore, is he?</b></font>

617
01:24:11,893 --> 01:24:13,224
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>What can I do?</b></font>

618
01:24:14,996 --> 01:24:17,260
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>You can go home now.</b></font>

619
01:24:19,234 --> 01:24:22,135
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I'd tell you to go and say goodbye,
but I've already been informed...</b></font>

620
01:24:22,337 --> 01:24:26,467
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>that for now all further contact
is out of the question.</b></font>

621
01:24:27,843 --> 01:24:29,003
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Right.</b></font>

622
01:25:07,549 --> 01:25:09,346
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Hi, Bruce. How you feeling?</b></font>

623
01:25:09,985 --> 01:25:11,919
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>The grub okay here for you?</b></font>

624
01:25:13,088 --> 01:25:15,921
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>- What do you want?
- That's a good question.</b></font>

625
01:25:17,058 --> 01:25:20,755
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I need your cells to trigger
some chemical distress signals...</b></font>

626
01:25:21,563 --> 01:25:24,760
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>so you can turn
a little green for me again...</b></font>

627
01:25:25,300 --> 01:25:28,269
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>and I can carve off a piece
of the real you...</b></font>

628
01:25:28,904 --> 01:25:31,771
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>analyze it, patent it
and make a fortune.</b></font>

629
01:25:33,175 --> 01:25:34,437
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>You mind?</b></font>

630
01:25:35,644 --> 01:25:37,373
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I'll never let you.</b></font>

631
01:25:38,113 --> 01:25:40,479
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I'm not sure
you've got much of a choice.</b></font>

632
01:25:42,651 --> 01:25:45,119
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Come on,
aren't you feeling a little angry?</b></font>

633
01:25:45,187 --> 01:25:46,821
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>After all,
you've only got me to play with...</b></font>

634
01:25:46,822 --> 01:25:50,349
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>now that Betty's dumped you
and gone back to Berkeley.</b></font>

635
01:25:50,492 --> 01:25:51,823
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>You're lying.</b></font>

636
01:25:51,927 --> 01:25:54,361
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>You know, for me,
this is a win-win situation.</b></font>

637
01:25:54,429 --> 01:25:56,864
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>You turn green, all these guys
come in and kill you...</b></font>

638
01:25:56,865 --> 01:25:59,459
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>and I perform the autopsy.
You don't...</b></font>

639
01:26:02,170 --> 01:26:03,865
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>and I mop the floor with you...</b></font>

640
01:26:03,939 --> 01:26:06,737
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>and maybe by accident
go too far and break your neck.</b></font>

641
01:26:06,808 --> 01:26:08,833
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>It's bad science, maybe...</b></font>

642
01:26:09,744 --> 01:26:11,336
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>but personally gratifying.</b></font>

643
01:26:13,548 --> 01:26:15,413
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Come on, Bruce.</b></font>

644
01:26:15,617 --> 01:26:17,517
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Let's see what you got.</b></font>

645
01:26:18,687 --> 01:26:19,847
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Never.</b></font>

646
01:26:25,961 --> 01:26:28,452
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>You know, consciously,
you may control it...</b></font>

647
01:26:29,030 --> 01:26:32,056
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>but subconsciously,
I bet that's another story.</b></font>

648
01:27:02,230 --> 01:27:05,290
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>All right,
let's jump-start those brain waves.</b></font>

649
01:27:31,993 --> 01:27:34,894
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>My dear Miss Ross, welcome back.</b></font>

650
01:27:36,464 --> 01:27:38,489
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>There are two guards right outside.</b></font>

651
01:27:38,567 --> 01:27:42,663
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>You don't have to worry.
I'm not angry with you, not anymore.</b></font>

652
01:27:44,706 --> 01:27:46,071
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>What do you want?</b></font>

653
01:27:46,341 --> 01:27:49,105
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>It's over for me now, I know that.</b></font>

654
01:27:49,744 --> 01:27:52,269
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>And soon it will be over for Bruce.</b></font>

655
01:27:53,949 --> 01:27:56,816
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>That's why I've come to you,
to ask you...</b></font>

656
01:27:57,552 --> 01:28:00,077
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>if you could persuade your father...</b></font>

657
01:28:00,155 --> 01:28:02,555
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>as a man, as a father himself...</b></font>

658
01:28:03,925 --> 01:28:07,452
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>that if I turn myself in now,
peacefully...</b></font>

659
01:28:07,862 --> 01:28:10,456
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>and before he
puts me away forever...</b></font>

660
01:28:11,132 --> 01:28:13,566
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>that he would let me see my son...</b></font>

661
01:28:14,436 --> 01:28:16,097
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>for one last time.</b></font>

662
01:28:17,172 --> 01:28:19,003
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Could you do that for me?</b></font>

663
01:28:22,510 --> 01:28:24,944
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>It's out of my father's hands now.</b></font>

664
01:28:29,684 --> 01:28:32,619
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I understand. He's a puppet now.</b></font>

665
01:28:34,255 --> 01:28:36,416
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>- I don't blame him.
- You shouldn't.</b></font>

666
01:28:37,158 --> 01:28:40,423
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>You should blame yourself
for what you've done to your son.</b></font>

667
01:28:41,396 --> 01:28:44,661
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>And what have I done to my son,
Miss Ross? Nothing.</b></font>

668
01:28:45,266 --> 01:28:48,929
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I tried to improve
on the limits in myself.</b></font>

669
01:28:49,604 --> 01:28:51,834
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Myself, not him.</b></font>

670
01:28:52,440 --> 01:28:53,998
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Can you understand?</b></font>

671
01:28:54,309 --> 01:28:56,573
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>To improve on nature. My nature.</b></font>

672
01:28:56,645 --> 01:29:00,911
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Knowledge of oneself.
It's the only path to the truth...</b></font>

673
01:29:01,316 --> 01:29:05,582
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>that gives men the power
to go beyond God's boundaries.</b></font>

674
01:29:06,788 --> 01:29:10,189
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>You know what's beyond
your boundaries? Other people.</b></font>

675
01:29:11,860 --> 01:29:14,158
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>All you've given Bruce is fear.</b></font>

676
01:29:16,598 --> 01:29:18,122
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>A fear of life.</b></font>

677
01:29:21,369 --> 01:29:22,461
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Fear?</b></font>

678
01:29:24,806 --> 01:29:26,671
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Perhaps, Miss Ross.</b></font>

679
01:29:28,910 --> 01:29:30,673
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>And loneliness, too.</b></font>

680
01:29:31,613 --> 01:29:32,602
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Yes.</b></font>

681
01:29:34,749 --> 01:29:36,376
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I feel them both.</b></font>

682
01:29:39,788 --> 01:29:41,517
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>But I have lived...</b></font>

683
01:29:42,824 --> 01:29:44,416
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>completely once.</b></font>

684
01:29:46,695 --> 01:29:48,560
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I was so much in love.</b></font>

685
01:29:49,831 --> 01:29:52,163
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>And she so much wanted a baby...</b></font>

686
01:29:52,767 --> 01:29:53,995
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>my baby.</b></font>

687
01:30:02,177 --> 01:30:05,010
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I could tell from the moment
she conceived...</b></font>

688
01:30:05,346 --> 01:30:07,940
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>that it wasn't a son
I had given her...</b></font>

689
01:30:08,183 --> 01:30:09,912
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>but something else.</b></font>

690
01:30:10,819 --> 01:30:12,446
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>A monster, maybe.</b></font>

691
01:30:12,821 --> 01:30:15,619
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I should have put a stop to it
right then...</b></font>

692
01:30:15,824 --> 01:30:17,587
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>but I was curious...</b></font>

693
01:30:18,159 --> 01:30:20,150
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>and that was my downfall.</b></font>

694
01:30:20,862 --> 01:30:24,161
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>And as I watched
this tiny life unfold...</b></font>

695
01:30:24,532 --> 01:30:27,365
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I began to imagine
the horror of it...</b></font>

696
01:30:28,269 --> 01:30:31,432
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>and my curiosity was replaced...</b></font>

697
01:30:32,707 --> 01:30:34,299
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>with compassion.</b></font>

698
01:30:37,245 --> 01:30:39,770
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>But they took away
my chance to cure him.</b></font>

699
01:30:39,848 --> 01:30:41,839
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Your father threw me out.</b></font>

700
01:30:43,585 --> 01:30:46,110
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I remember that day so well...</b></font>

701
01:30:46,187 --> 01:30:48,849
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>every moment, every sensation.</b></font>

702
01:30:48,990 --> 01:30:50,651
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Walking into the house...</b></font>

703
01:30:50,992 --> 01:30:54,325
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>the feeling of the handle
of the knife in my hand.</b></font>

704
01:30:54,529 --> 01:30:57,089
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I knew I was doing
a father's work...</b></font>

705
01:30:57,298 --> 01:30:59,596
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>fulfilling a father's Mercy.</b></font>

706
01:30:59,868 --> 01:31:02,496
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>David, please stop it! No!</b></font>

707
01:31:02,737 --> 01:31:04,568
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>David, talk to me!</b></font>

708
01:31:06,040 --> 01:31:08,065
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>But then she surprised me.</b></font>

709
01:31:15,116 --> 01:31:16,447
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>It was as if...</b></font>

710
01:31:17,485 --> 01:31:19,953
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>she and the knife...</b></font>

711
01:31:21,656 --> 01:31:23,021
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>merged.</b></font>

712
01:31:32,801 --> 01:31:33,825
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Go!</b></font>

713
01:31:34,269 --> 01:31:36,430
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>You cannot imagine...</b></font>

714
01:31:37,205 --> 01:31:40,641
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>the unbearable finality of it.</b></font>

715
01:31:42,110 --> 01:31:44,271
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>And in that one moment...</b></font>

716
01:31:44,846 --> 01:31:47,974
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I took everything
that was dear to me...</b></font>

717
01:31:49,250 --> 01:31:51,047
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>and transformed it...</b></font>

718
01:31:51,419 --> 01:31:54,877
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>into nothing more than a memory.</b></font>

719
01:32:10,872 --> 01:32:14,035
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Bingo! That must be some
jumbo nightmare he just had.</b></font>

720
01:32:19,147 --> 01:32:21,445
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Do it now.
Start the enzyme extraction.</b></font>

721
01:32:26,421 --> 01:32:28,548
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Sir, negative on drill penetration.</b></font>

722
01:32:28,623 --> 01:32:31,990
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Damn it, drill him harder.
Give me full RPMs. Come on.</b></font>

723
01:32:46,040 --> 01:32:47,871
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>- Should I neutralize?
- No!</b></font>

724
01:32:47,942 --> 01:32:50,274
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I can't do anything with goop.
Come on!</b></font>

725
01:33:03,591 --> 01:33:04,751
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>All right, put him to sleep.</b></font>

726
01:33:15,603 --> 01:33:17,195
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>It's not stopping him!</b></font>

727
01:33:24,178 --> 01:33:27,875
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Ready room, send in our
containment team, non-lethals only.</b></font>

728
01:33:27,949 --> 01:33:31,180
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I repeat, non-lethals only.
I must have a sample of him.</b></font>

729
01:33:31,786 --> 01:33:32,946
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Sir!</b></font>

730
01:33:35,556 --> 01:33:36,716
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Jesus.</b></font>

731
01:33:37,625 --> 01:33:40,389
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>- Use the foam.
- Deploy containment foam.</b></font>

732
01:33:41,729 --> 01:33:43,458
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Talbot, talk to me.</b></font>

733
01:33:44,999 --> 01:33:46,023
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Cease fire!</b></font>

734
01:33:46,100 --> 01:33:48,762
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Under control, General.
I'll let you know if we need you.</b></font>

735
01:33:48,836 --> 01:33:51,703
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Unacceptable. Unseat your asses
down there immediately.</b></font>

736
01:33:51,773 --> 01:33:54,674
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I want a full evacuation now.
I'm shutting you down.</b></font>

737
01:33:54,742 --> 01:33:55,868
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Lock down.</b></font>

738
01:33:56,311 --> 01:33:59,109
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>- Didn't you hear the General?
- I said lock down!</b></font>

739
01:34:01,983 --> 01:34:04,213
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Clear! I need a sample of him!</b></font>

740
01:34:06,621 --> 01:34:09,852
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>All right,
take it easy there, buddy.</b></font>

741
01:34:10,325 --> 01:34:13,123
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>This might give you
a bit of a sting here, Bruce.</b></font>

742
01:34:26,007 --> 01:34:27,235
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Fall back!</b></font>

743
01:34:27,775 --> 01:34:30,209
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Clear your weapon!
Give me the M2.</b></font>

744
01:34:30,878 --> 01:34:32,505
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>So long, big boy.</b></font>

745
01:34:32,847 --> 01:34:34,007
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Clear!</b></font>

746
01:34:45,293 --> 01:34:47,921
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Lock down
the entire facility immediately.</b></font>

747
01:34:52,600 --> 01:34:55,160
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Target still moving
towards blue level.</b></font>

748
01:34:55,236 --> 01:34:56,863
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Evacuate the main hall.</b></font>

749
01:35:03,311 --> 01:35:06,678
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Send in backup, heavy weapons.
Issue general quarters.</b></font>

750
01:35:34,242 --> 01:35:36,472
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Contamination, Sir.
System readings are redline.</b></font>

751
01:35:36,544 --> 01:35:38,478
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Stand by
for backup power supply.</b></font>

752
01:35:45,386 --> 01:35:46,648
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Incoming!</b></font>

753
01:35:54,695 --> 01:35:57,163
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>- Shut down power to the main hall.
- Sir?</b></font>

754
01:35:57,498 --> 01:36:00,831
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Show him the way out.
We'll fight him outside.</b></font>

755
01:38:10,631 --> 01:38:13,065
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Driver, stop.</b></font>

756
01:38:20,474 --> 01:38:22,704
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Gunner! Traverse right!</b></font>

757
01:40:02,176 --> 01:40:05,873
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Mr. President,
I have some bad news, Sir.</b></font>

758
01:40:06,247 --> 01:40:07,839
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Let's have it, General.</b></font>

759
01:40:07,915 --> 01:40:09,644
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I've briefed the President
on Angry Man.</b></font>

760
01:40:09,717 --> 01:40:11,241
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I assume that's what this is about.</b></font>

761
01:40:11,419 --> 01:40:12,647
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Lt is, ma'am.</b></font>

762
01:40:12,720 --> 01:40:15,814
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I'm requesting a National
Command Authority override.</b></font>

763
01:40:16,123 --> 01:40:18,489
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Angry Man is unsecure.</b></font>

764
01:40:19,160 --> 01:40:23,324
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I need everything we have
at my disposal to stop his movement.</b></font>

765
01:40:23,864 --> 01:40:26,492
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>You're expecting
civilian casualties, General?</b></font>

766
01:40:26,934 --> 01:40:28,765
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Not if I can help it, ma'am.</b></font>

767
01:40:29,203 --> 01:40:31,569
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Consider it done. Keep us posted.</b></font>

768
01:41:20,254 --> 01:41:22,188
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Contact Goodman Control.</b></font>

769
01:41:22,523 --> 01:41:24,423
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Patch data to the assets.</b></font>

770
01:41:24,925 --> 01:41:26,449
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Contact HQ.</b></font>

771
01:41:27,261 --> 01:41:30,355
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Have them initiate
an immediate evacuation...</b></font>

772
01:41:31,132 --> 01:41:35,592
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>in the vicinity
of grid coordinates 6-5...</b></font>

773
01:42:11,038 --> 01:42:13,506
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Confirm that the area
has been cleared.</b></font>

774
01:42:13,574 --> 01:42:14,941
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Confirm area cleared.</b></font>

775
01:42:14,942 --> 01:42:18,343
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>HQ confirms area cleared.
Assets on-line, Sir.</b></font>

776
01:42:18,479 --> 01:42:20,470
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Gentlemen, it's time to dig in.</b></font>

777
01:42:20,781 --> 01:42:23,807
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I want this target
stopped in his tracks.</b></font>

778
01:43:14,668 --> 01:43:15,726
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Jesus.</b></font>

779
01:43:31,752 --> 01:43:33,083
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Mayday!</b></font>

780
01:43:33,654 --> 01:43:34,712
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Shit!</b></font>

781
01:43:40,761 --> 01:43:43,924
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Tango-4 is down.
Have C-SAR respond to our 20 now.</b></font>

782
01:43:46,600 --> 01:43:48,659
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Get him off us
before he tears us apart!</b></font>

783
01:43:48,736 --> 01:43:51,227
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I've got no shot!
You have a line of fire?</b></font>

784
01:43:52,172 --> 01:43:54,163
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>- Watch it, Tango.
- Break left!</b></font>

785
01:43:57,144 --> 01:43:59,806
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Tango-3, pull back
and set up for a Hellfire shot.</b></font>

786
01:43:59,880 --> 01:44:02,371
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Hold your fire
until we draw him off.</b></font>

787
01:44:02,650 --> 01:44:04,345
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Tango-1 is hot.</b></font>

788
01:44:04,785 --> 01:44:06,685
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Roger. Going hot. Guns ready.</b></font>

789
01:44:12,560 --> 01:44:13,959
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Engage at will.</b></font>

790
01:44:34,782 --> 01:44:36,977
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Tango-1, pull back! Clear my line!</b></font>

791
01:44:37,818 --> 01:44:40,787
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Tango-flight, clear.
I have him painted for Hellfire.</b></font>

792
01:44:43,490 --> 01:44:45,481
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Tango-1 clear. Take the shot.</b></font>

793
01:45:04,445 --> 01:45:06,777
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Tango-1, Tango-3, I have contact.</b></font>

794
01:45:07,381 --> 01:45:09,372
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Holy shit! He's got my missile!</b></font>

795
01:45:11,885 --> 01:45:13,147
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Mayday!</b></font>

796
01:45:16,090 --> 01:45:18,752
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Mayday! We're hit! We're going down!</b></font>

797
01:45:22,997 --> 01:45:25,261
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>- Give me a head count.
- Tango-3.</b></font>

798
01:45:27,835 --> 01:45:30,429
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Our kite's busted up,
but we're okay.</b></font>

799
01:45:32,773 --> 01:45:35,241
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Tango-flight,
you have eyes on the target?</b></font>

800
01:45:36,176 --> 01:45:38,235
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Tango-1, I have him in the rocks.</b></font>

801
01:45:38,312 --> 01:45:40,746
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Salvo all.
Turn it into a parking lot.</b></font>

802
01:46:02,002 --> 01:46:04,129
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>T-bolt, your parking lot is ready.</b></font>

803
01:46:04,371 --> 01:46:06,771
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>We're bingo for fuel and ammo. RTB.</b></font>

804
01:46:34,735 --> 01:46:38,466
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>T-bolt.
Be advised, target not destroyed.</b></font>

805
01:46:38,706 --> 01:46:40,333
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>He's on the move again.</b></font>

806
01:46:40,407 --> 01:46:41,396
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Damn!</b></font>

807
01:46:42,076 --> 01:46:43,475
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I've got it.</b></font>

808
01:46:44,478 --> 01:46:46,673
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>It appears he's heading home.</b></font>

809
01:46:47,614 --> 01:46:51,175
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Launch fast movers.
Have them intercept and engage.</b></font>

810
01:46:54,054 --> 01:46:57,023
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>- Hello?
- Betty, Bruce got out.</b></font>

811
01:46:57,524 --> 01:47:00,425
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>He's headed your way,
probably right for you.</b></font>

812
01:47:00,694 --> 01:47:02,423
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>How far from the base are you?</b></font>

813
01:47:02,496 --> 01:47:05,624
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I'm already here.
They're taking his father in now.</b></font>

814
01:47:06,200 --> 01:47:07,827
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>That's all good news.</b></font>

815
01:47:08,135 --> 01:47:09,693
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Stay there, Betty.</b></font>

816
01:47:23,951 --> 01:47:26,749
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Legend-1 rolling in hot.
Legend-2 breaking left.</b></font>

817
01:47:27,387 --> 01:47:30,117
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I think I can come
back around for a gun attack.</b></font>

818
01:47:30,824 --> 01:47:33,418
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Acquire a clear target.
Fire at will.</b></font>

819
01:47:38,732 --> 01:47:41,530
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Increase altitude.
Civilian aircraft in vicinity.</b></font>

820
01:47:46,807 --> 01:47:49,537
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Pull up!
You're headed for the bridge!</b></font>

821
01:47:51,378 --> 01:47:53,505
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I can't pull up!</b></font>

822
01:48:02,456 --> 01:48:05,323
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>You got him. Take him
on a ride to the top of the world.</b></font>

823
01:48:05,392 --> 01:48:07,917
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Let's see what the thin air
will do for him.</b></font>

824
01:48:09,163 --> 01:48:10,687
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Initiating afterburn.</b></font>

825
01:48:28,382 --> 01:48:30,282
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I'm passing Flight Level 600.</b></font>

826
01:48:30,851 --> 01:48:32,648
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>This is out of my envelope.</b></font>

827
01:48:33,053 --> 01:48:34,645
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Hang in there, Legend.</b></font>

828
01:48:34,721 --> 01:48:37,588
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I can't maintain.
He's all over my aerodynamics.</b></font>

829
01:48:37,791 --> 01:48:40,089
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>He'll lose consciousness before you.</b></font>

830
01:48:44,097 --> 01:48:45,724
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>950.</b></font>

831
01:48:45,999 --> 01:48:48,866
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I can't hold it. I'm pulling back.</b></font>

832
01:49:36,516 --> 01:49:38,108
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Puny human.</b></font>

833
01:49:48,339 --> 01:49:50,963
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Contact. He's in the water.
All units, weapons hot.</b></font>

834
01:49:50,964 --> 01:49:52,693
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Let's not take any chances.</b></font>

835
01:49:52,766 --> 01:49:55,564
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>You are cleared
to fire on target, Legend.</b></font>

836
01:50:18,125 --> 01:50:19,456
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>- Dad?
- Betty?</b></font>

837
01:50:20,894 --> 01:50:22,521
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>We don't have a choice.</b></font>

838
01:50:22,863 --> 01:50:24,296
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I have to destroy him.</b></font>

839
01:50:24,364 --> 01:50:25,524
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>But you can't.</b></font>

840
01:50:25,599 --> 01:50:28,500
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>You'll only fuel his rage
and make him stronger.</b></font>

841
01:50:30,103 --> 01:50:32,571
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>It's you he's coming for,
you know that.</b></font>

842
01:50:34,574 --> 01:50:36,439
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Then let me go to him.</b></font>

843
01:50:37,444 --> 01:50:38,638
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Please.</b></font>

844
01:50:40,547 --> 01:50:43,038
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Just give him a chance to calm down.</b></font>

845
01:51:02,469 --> 01:51:05,495
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>All aircraft
vicinity San Francisco...</b></font>

846
01:51:05,572 --> 01:51:07,472
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>this is T-bolt on guard.</b></font>

847
01:51:07,808 --> 01:51:11,073
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>This area has been declared
restricted airspace.</b></font>

848
01:51:11,345 --> 01:51:15,304
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>All aircraft are ordered
to clear the airspace immediately.</b></font>

849
01:51:57,391 --> 01:52:00,053
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Echo-19, weapons are hot.
Target acquired.</b></font>

850
01:52:00,127 --> 01:52:02,061
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Waiting your orders to engage.</b></font>

851
01:52:05,065 --> 01:52:07,727
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Command code yellow.
Hold for authorization.</b></font>

852
01:52:17,911 --> 01:52:19,572
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>All units, hold your fire.</b></font>

853
01:52:19,646 --> 01:52:23,082
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>T-bolt to all assets.
You have direct orders to hold your fire.</b></font>

854
01:52:23,150 --> 01:52:25,015
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I repeat. Hold your fire.</b></font>

855
01:52:44,404 --> 01:52:45,496
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Move now!</b></font>

856
01:52:54,448 --> 01:52:56,473
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Everybody down! Down!</b></font>

857
01:54:29,442 --> 01:54:30,909
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>You found me.</b></font>

858
01:54:33,213 --> 01:54:35,443
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>You weren't that hard to find.</b></font>

859
01:54:37,851 --> 01:54:39,216
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Yes, I was.</b></font>

860
01:56:19,085 --> 01:56:20,882
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>That's the deal, gentlemen.</b></font>

861
01:56:21,454 --> 01:56:24,423
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>He stays on this base until
we get the final word from C-3...</b></font>

862
01:56:24,491 --> 01:56:26,220
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>on how to dispose of him.</b></font>

863
01:56:26,826 --> 01:56:30,193
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>In the meantime, if he does
anything but sit in that chair...</b></font>

864
01:56:32,299 --> 01:56:35,894
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>we'll turn on the juice and
he'll be incinerated immediately.</b></font>

865
01:56:36,069 --> 01:56:38,594
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>We've established
a 200-yard perimeter, Sir.</b></font>

866
01:56:39,005 --> 01:56:41,166
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>If we deploy
the electromagnetic array...</b></font>

867
01:56:41,241 --> 01:56:43,402
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>there should be
no collateral damage.</b></font>

868
01:56:52,419 --> 01:56:54,649
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I'm doing this for you, Betty.</b></font>

869
01:56:54,888 --> 01:56:58,517
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>But one way or another, we're gonna
have to prepare for the worst.</b></font>

870
01:58:48,401 --> 01:58:50,392
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>L should have killed you.</b></font>

871
01:58:51,538 --> 01:58:53,665
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>As I should have killed you.</b></font>

872
01:58:55,208 --> 01:58:56,732
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I wish you had.</b></font>

873
01:59:02,849 --> 01:59:04,646
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I saw her last night.</b></font>

874
01:59:06,986 --> 01:59:08,453
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Saw her face.</b></font>

875
01:59:09,722 --> 01:59:11,189
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Brown hair...</b></font>

876
01:59:13,159 --> 01:59:14,524
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>brown eyes.</b></font>

877
01:59:16,062 --> 01:59:17,654
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>She smiled at me.</b></font>

878
01:59:19,065 --> 01:59:21,659
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>She reached down
and kissed my cheek.</b></font>

879
01:59:23,770 --> 01:59:26,102
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I can almost remember a smell.</b></font>

880
01:59:30,376 --> 01:59:32,469
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>It was like desert flowers.</b></font>

881
01:59:34,614 --> 01:59:36,411
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Her favorite perfume.</b></font>

882
01:59:39,752 --> 01:59:41,242
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>It's my Mother...</b></font>

883
01:59:41,921 --> 01:59:44,219
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>and I don't even know her name.</b></font>

884
01:59:51,731 --> 01:59:53,494
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>It's all right, son.</b></font>

885
01:59:54,167 --> 01:59:55,964
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Go ahead and cry.</b></font>

886
02:00:08,515 --> 02:00:11,951
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>- Cry. Crying will do you good.
- Don't touch me!</b></font>

887
02:00:15,355 --> 02:00:17,585
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Maybe once you were my father.</b></font>

888
02:00:18,658 --> 02:00:20,922
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>But you're not now
and you never will be.</b></font>

889
02:00:21,661 --> 02:00:23,026
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Ls that so?</b></font>

890
02:00:24,964 --> 02:00:26,955
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Well, I got news for you.</b></font>

891
02:00:27,367 --> 02:00:29,767
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I didn't come here to see you.</b></font>

892
02:00:30,703 --> 02:00:33,035
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I came here to see my son.</b></font>

893
02:00:34,607 --> 02:00:36,074
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>My real son.</b></font>

894
02:00:36,843 --> 02:00:38,708
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>The one inside of you.</b></font>

895
02:00:39,779 --> 02:00:43,476
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>You're nothing
but a superficial shell...</b></font>

896
02:00:43,550 --> 02:00:46,041
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>a husk of flimsy consciousness...</b></font>

897
02:00:46,152 --> 02:00:49,178
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>ready to be torn off
at a moment's notice.</b></font>

898
02:00:49,489 --> 02:00:52,754
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>You can think what you like.
I don't care. Just go.</b></font>

899
02:00:58,831 --> 02:01:01,891
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>No, son, listen to me.
I found a cure.</b></font>

900
02:01:03,136 --> 02:01:04,330
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>For me.</b></font>

901
02:01:05,138 --> 02:01:07,368
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>My cells can transform, too...</b></font>

902
02:01:07,874 --> 02:01:10,308
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>absorb enormous amounts of energy.</b></font>

903
02:01:10,777 --> 02:01:13,211
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>But, unlike you, they're unstable.</b></font>

904
02:01:13,613 --> 02:01:14,773
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Son...</b></font>

905
02:01:15,515 --> 02:01:17,073
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I need your strength.</b></font>

906
02:01:18,451 --> 02:01:20,476
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I gave you life.</b></font>

907
02:01:20,987 --> 02:01:23,820
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Now you must give it back to me...</b></font>

908
02:01:24,958 --> 02:01:28,485
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>only a million times more radiant...</b></font>

909
02:01:28,561 --> 02:01:29,960
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>more powerful.</b></font>

910
02:01:30,530 --> 02:01:32,930
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>- Stop!
- Stop what?</b></font>

911
02:01:33,366 --> 02:01:35,095
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Stop what?</b></font>

912
02:01:36,135 --> 02:01:40,196
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Think of all those men out there
in their uniforms...</b></font>

913
02:01:40,807 --> 02:01:43,571
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>barking and swallowing orders!</b></font>

914
02:01:43,943 --> 02:01:47,344
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Inflicting their petty rule
over the entire globe!</b></font>

915
02:01:47,947 --> 02:01:50,438
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Think of all the harm they've done!</b></font>

916
02:01:51,117 --> 02:01:53,278
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>To you! To me!</b></font>

917
02:01:54,087 --> 02:01:55,520
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>To humanity!</b></font>

918
02:01:56,422 --> 02:01:59,289
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>And know this,
that we can make them...</b></font>

919
02:01:59,359 --> 02:02:02,089
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>and their flags, their anthems
and their governments...</b></font>

920
02:02:02,161 --> 02:02:04,493
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>disappear in a flash!</b></font>

921
02:02:04,797 --> 02:02:06,287
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>You in me.</b></font>

922
02:02:06,699 --> 02:02:07,996
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I'd rather die.</b></font>

923
02:02:11,137 --> 02:02:12,798
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>That's your answer?</b></font>

924
02:02:13,539 --> 02:02:15,666
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Then indeed you shall die...</b></font>

925
02:02:16,175 --> 02:02:19,042
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>and be reborn a hero...</b></font>

926
02:02:19,846 --> 02:02:21,939
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>of the kind that walked the Earth...</b></font>

927
02:02:22,015 --> 02:02:25,507
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>long before the pale religions
of civilization...</b></font>

928
02:02:25,952 --> 02:02:28,352
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>infected humanity's soul!</b></font>

929
02:02:28,588 --> 02:02:31,022
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Go!</b></font>

930
02:02:46,406 --> 02:02:48,169
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Stop your bawling...</b></font>

931
02:02:49,008 --> 02:02:51,602
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>you weak little speck
of human trash.</b></font>

932
02:03:00,386 --> 02:03:01,444
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I'll go.</b></font>

933
02:03:03,122 --> 02:03:04,953
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>You just watch me go!</b></font>

934
02:03:05,391 --> 02:03:06,380
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Hit it!</b></font>

935
02:03:32,218 --> 02:03:33,947
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>- Hit it again.
- We can't, Sir.</b></font>

936
02:03:34,020 --> 02:03:37,353
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>There's no power. Some kind of
counter electromagnetic field.</b></font>

937
02:03:42,295 --> 02:03:44,490
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Move in and assault the target.
Move in!</b></font>

938
02:04:36,916 --> 02:04:39,407
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Sir, I've located them on radar.
Pear Lake.</b></font>

939
02:04:39,786 --> 02:04:41,754
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Call up the task force.</b></font>

940
02:04:49,095 --> 02:04:50,426
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Yes.</b></font>

941
02:05:55,895 --> 02:05:58,261
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>That's right. Keep fighting.</b></font>

942
02:05:59,365 --> 02:06:02,801
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>The more you fight,
the more of you I take.</b></font>

943
02:06:11,477 --> 02:06:12,774
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Strange.</b></font>

944
02:06:12,879 --> 02:06:15,939
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>We're reading a phenomenal drop
in temperatures there...</b></font>

945
02:06:16,015 --> 02:06:18,381
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>with simultaneous
radiological activity.</b></font>

946
02:06:18,517 --> 02:06:21,247
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>They're absorbing
all the ambient energy.</b></font>

947
02:06:29,896 --> 02:06:31,056
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Relax.</b></font>

948
02:06:31,464 --> 02:06:34,558
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Sleep now, Bruce,
and forget forever.</b></font>

949
02:06:35,234 --> 02:06:36,792
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Struggle no more...</b></font>

950
02:06:37,136 --> 02:06:40,128
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>and give me all of your power.</b></font>

951
02:06:41,874 --> 02:06:44,741
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>You think you can live with it?
Take it!</b></font>

952
02:06:46,078 --> 02:06:48,842
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Take it all!</b></font>

953
02:06:51,083 --> 02:06:52,516
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Yes.</b></font>

954
02:07:08,401 --> 02:07:09,868
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Take it back.</b></font>

955
02:07:12,204 --> 02:07:14,570
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>It's not stopping!</b></font>

956
02:07:15,508 --> 02:07:17,408
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Take it back!</b></font>

957
02:07:34,026 --> 02:07:36,517
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Gentlemen, release.</b></font>

958
02:07:44,804 --> 02:07:46,465
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Gamma charge away.</b></font>

959
02:08:11,597 --> 02:08:13,064
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Sweet dreams.</b></font>

960
02:08:31,117 --> 02:08:35,417
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>ONE YEAR LATER...</b></font>

961
02:09:06,752 --> 02:09:08,913
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>- Hello?
- Betty? Is that you?</b></font>

962
02:09:09,321 --> 02:09:10,413
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Hi, Dad.</b></font>

963
02:09:10,756 --> 02:09:12,280
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I'm glad I caught you.</b></font>

964
02:09:12,358 --> 02:09:14,656
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>- I'm glad you called.
- Thanks.</b></font>

965
02:09:17,029 --> 02:09:18,519
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Look, Betty...</b></font>

966
02:09:19,498 --> 02:09:20,726
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>you and I...</b></font>

967
02:09:21,734 --> 02:09:23,258
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>We both know that Bruce...</b></font>

968
02:09:23,335 --> 02:09:25,462
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>couldn't have survived that blast.</b></font>

969
02:09:26,505 --> 02:09:28,837
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>But... Well, you know...</b></font>

970
02:09:30,910 --> 02:09:32,275
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>What is it?</b></font>

971
02:09:32,745 --> 02:09:34,940
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>You know, the usual loonies...</b></font>

972
02:09:35,714 --> 02:09:38,581
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>seeing things,
only now everything's green.</b></font>

973
02:09:40,853 --> 02:09:41,979
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Right.</b></font>

974
02:09:42,922 --> 02:09:44,116
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Look...</b></font>

975
02:09:45,758 --> 02:09:48,283
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>if by some chance he did survive...</b></font>

976
02:09:49,895 --> 02:09:53,626
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>and he should try to contact you,
and try to get in touch...</b></font>

977
02:09:54,800 --> 02:09:56,927
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>you'd tell me, wouldn't you?</b></font>

978
02:09:58,070 --> 02:10:00,436
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>No. I wouldn't.</b></font>

979
02:10:02,074 --> 02:10:05,237
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>But you know as well as I do
I wouldn't have to.</b></font>

980
02:10:05,311 --> 02:10:07,871
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I mean, my phones are bugged...</b></font>

981
02:10:07,947 --> 02:10:10,939
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>my computer is tapped,
I'm under surveillance.</b></font>

982
02:10:13,552 --> 02:10:15,315
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I'll tell you, though...</b></font>

983
02:10:15,821 --> 02:10:17,822
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>that if he were alive...</b></font>

984
02:10:17,823 --> 02:10:21,126
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I'm the last person
I would want him to come to...</b></font>

985
02:10:21,127 --> 02:10:25,962
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>because, as much as I Miss him...</b></font>

986
02:10:27,600 --> 02:10:29,227
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I loved him.</b></font>

987
02:10:36,942 --> 02:10:38,569
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I'm sorry, Betty.</b></font>

988
02:10:40,579 --> 02:10:42,069
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I am so sorry.</b></font>

989
02:10:45,518 --> 02:10:47,042
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I know you are.</b></font>

990
02:11:20,452 --> 02:11:23,785
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Listen to your father
and take your medicine, okay?</b></font>

991
02:11:38,704 --> 02:11:40,194
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Take all the medicine.</b></font>

992
02:11:41,707 --> 02:11:42,833
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Quiet!</b></font>

993
02:11:44,009 --> 02:11:45,306
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Sit down!</b></font>

994
02:11:45,377 --> 02:11:46,366
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Shut up!</b></font>

995
02:11:49,481 --> 02:11:53,008
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>We need these medicines
for the people who live here.</b></font>

996
02:11:53,485 --> 02:11:56,283
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Who are you to decide
what the people need?</b></font>

997
02:11:56,822 --> 02:12:00,121
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>These people are helping
our enemies.</b></font>

998
02:12:01,627 --> 02:12:04,095
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>And maybe you are too.</b></font>

999
02:12:04,663 --> 02:12:05,823
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Take all this.</b></font>

1000
02:12:06,465 --> 02:12:09,366
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>It is the property
of the government.</b></font>

1001
02:12:11,337 --> 02:12:13,100
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>You're making me angry.</b></font>

1002
02:12:15,207 --> 02:12:17,675
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>You wouldn't like me when I'm angry.</b></font>

